Ethel's mysteries

These photos were all found among Ethel Maud McKague's pictures--but do not have proper identification on them. Many of the people look familiar, but we cannot put names to them. If you can identify ANY of these people (and/or correct our guesses), please let Linda know as soon as possible. (Most of these will be from William McKague's line or McGregors as far as we know.) Click on the small picture to see a large version. Any available information and/or guesses appear at the bottom of each large picture. Use the "back" button on your browser to return to this page.
